# T1g — blocked-pattern loop `break` (L193) ReplaceBreakWithContinue. Once a
# pattern matches, has_blocked=True is set; continuing only re-scans the
# remaining patterns, leaving has_blocked True. The return value
# _classify_command_tier_cached(command, has_blocked) is identical.
core/ReplaceBreakWithContinue|193:12-193:17|0
